About Zitler

Meet Akash

Founded by Akash, Zitler represents the convergence of technology, entrepreneurship, and education. We believe in empowering people and organizations through innovative solutions and accessible learning.

Our mission is simple: partner with ambitious startups, build cutting-edge products, and break down educational barriers so anyone can learn and grow in technology.

Startup Partnership

We've partnered with numerous startups, providing technical expertise, strategic guidance, and hands-on support to help them succeed.

Active Development

Running multiple successful ventures across various tech domains, from SaaS platforms to AI-powered solutions.

Education Without Barriers

Providing practical, skill-focused learning that doesn't require certificatesjust dedication and curiosity.

Frequently Asked Questions

What does Zitler do?

Zitler is a technology company that partners with startups, develops innovative products, and provides accessible education. We work across the entire tech lifecyclefrom ideation to execution.

How does the education program work?

Our programs focus on practical skills and real-world application, not credentials. We believe in barrier-free learning where anyone can acquire tech skills without formal certificates.

How can Zitler help my startup?

We provide end-to-end partnership including technical development, strategic planning, and access to our network of resources to help your startup succeed.

What technologies do you specialize in?

We work with modern tech stacks including React, Node.js, Python, cloud platforms (AWS, Google Cloud), AI/ML frameworks, and emerging technologies.

How can I get in touch?

You can reach us through our contact form below or email us directly. We're always open to discussing new opportunities and partnerships.
